name: Resume - The Point Blue
description:
Stand out from the rest with this clean and modern resume design. This is not a printed product. You will receive a high resolution PDF of your resume. How It works
Once your payment is accepted you will be directed to a confirmation page that has a link to a form where you can upload your current resume or fill out with your resume information. I will then send you a proof of your resume. You may make any changes as necessary. As soon as you are happy with your resume I will send you your final PDF copy of the resume.
